  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  type 1 diabetes for more than 6 months

          -  on insulin pump or multiple daily injections without plans to change modality in next
             6 months

          -  insured by CCS or Medi-Cal

          -  receiving care at Lucile Packard Children's Hospital or Stanford Children's Health
             outpatient clinics

          -  English or Spanish-speaking

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  major illness or condition that may alter glucose control or ability to complete the
             study including pregnancy, cystic fibrosis, cancer, liver disease, history of
             transplant, or hemoglobinopathy

          -  current oral glucocorticoid use

          -  prior use of a CGM system

          -  hemoglobin A1C &lt;7.5% or &gt;12%

          -  no wireless internet access
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
